{"tid":1613223,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[華為打手請入]  封後門 華為Mate 30 Pro未能手動安裝Google","createTime":"2019-10-02T13:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:57.000Z","uid":42246,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b664a55e80a0267711dca71ac55ba64473044717","tid":1613223,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:15:03.000Z","msg":"《彭博通訊社》報道，雖然美國針對華為的禁令禁止公司使用美國的零件及軟件，包括是Google Maps及Gmail等，但有保安專家指出華為新推出的Mate 30 Pro手機能容許用戶手動下載及安裝Google的應用程式。<br />\n<br />\n事件曝光後一些智能手機專家反映，Mate 30設備突然不能手動安裝安卓應用程式，據悉相關行動只有Google能夠進行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外岩岩睇緊微博 有片睇海外Mate 30已經用唔到google pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a55cd4ffe9c81255562e1cad652a7590f8f874","tid":1613223,"uid":16344,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:20:25.000Z","msg":"去香討取笑班共奴仲好玩啦"},{"pid":"1916097b4cdc91d4fda43bf4b044d02cb24f4a52","tid":1613223,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bca248ed8541199c7fddd8d6875b72a068293dc","tid":1613223,"uid":34213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:28:23.000Z","msg":"入黎睇睇先，成皮野買垃圾值得一讚"},{"pid":"8fae32a9824242a3635e207927b0dc9beabe5c13","tid":1613223,"uid":11428,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:51:31.000Z","msg":"Android 要裝返應該唔難，時間問題<br />\n<br />\n送都唔會用"},{"pid":"ccbc5ec548858288058b456d6aae57bb076583b3","tid":1613223,"uid":18947,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8fae32a9824242a3635e207927b0dc9beabe5c13","tid":1613223,"uid":11428,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"repl