ji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e3f93dcfcf5e837a9ec2c7aa305e9435162d98","tid":1613223,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:49:02.000Z","msg":"「TaiwanWarmPower」今晚（15日）在臉書發文，呼籲民眾一同連署「德國聯邦議會第95643號請願書」 ，支持「請求德國與中華民國（台灣）建立外交關係」，內文中指出迫害人權的中共不應代表民主自由的台灣。小編表示，可參考連署教學影片，2分鐘左右的時間就能完成簽署，如能在10月9日前達成5萬人連署，就有機會將此議題送進德國國會。<br />\n<br />\n#AntiChinazi<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2916703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2916703&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=8f3e3168\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2916703&h=2efc4681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2916703</a><br />\n<br />\n連署教學from TW:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/allen.taiwangermany/videos/pcb.2942668175748064/2942643702417178/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fallen.taiwangermany%2Fvideos%2Fpcb.2942668175748064%2F2942643702417178%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=a726dde2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/allen.taiwangermany/videos/pcb.2942668175748064/2942643702417178/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n連署link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_05/_31/Petition_95643.mitzeichnen.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_05%2F_31%2FPetition_95643.mitzeichnen.html&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=412af69f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_05/_31/Petition_95643.mitzeichnen.html</a><br />\n<br />\n大家幫下手, 聯台灣抗邪惡強国<br />\n<br />\n仲爭1400咋"},{"pid":"ac9850ed495e93e79c3e142bb29c1d711cdc7271","tid":1613223,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d15a5d6a6f95d129692c10980499695e43960569","tid":1613223,"uid":255744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:58:58.000Z","msg":"10月5號晚條On99深藍絲又出片講番呢件事同講佢用唔到Google pay功能。佢話唔係Google主動封鎖該個網站，呢點佢啱。但之後佢講到搵點解用唔到Google pay起因時可能諗太多諗錯晒方向。<br />\n以下講嘅要對Android 7起root機有點認知嘅可能就明我講乜&hellip;<br />\n佢片中用咗個app叫Safety status test，test有邊幾樣唔通過會Fail，佢見到CTS profile match fail咗，之後佢影片如下嘅一半時間就開始諗錯方向&hellip;<br />\n我睇完佢片，嘗試用Google Search：CTS profile match ，打字Search時打到一半見到有關鍵搜尋發現「CTS profile match 解決」咦！ 有中文喎，就以呢個關鍵詞去搵，搵到一個Link係台灣ptt ，而該篇ptt文完全講解咗啲大陸國行An機點解去到呢一步就fail過唔到嘅因由。而我睇完，我當然知佢點解佢部國行mate 30 pro用唔到Google pay啦。<br />\n<br />\n再講一次，如果對An機root機有少少研究都知，Android7之後如果要root，一定要得到該廠或第三方嘅unlock bootloader方法嘅程式碼(key)， unlock咗先可以用Magisk去root，之後再刷MagiskHide模組就順利通過CTS profile match test就可以繞過Google SafetyNet驗証，可以用到Google pay。問題係華為禁止佢旗下手機unlock bootloader來企途root機。咁呢件On99藍絲枉佢仲係屎為忠粉曾幫屎為部p30 pro月亮mode係P出咗拍片辯解過。而佢跟官咁耐，連官都唔畀佢蒙面佢未撚知？？？ 最少笑撚死我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後就係如果有意買國行機(如ASUS ROG Phone2)如果有該牌子嘅專用UI(如小米miui、華為emui)等等嘅手機，要睇吓嗰一個牌子有冇替旗下手機係root方面或第三方(如XDA)有提供方式可以unlock BL然後root，如果無，就算點樣幫你刷入GMS，都算係呃到人嘅GMS。真係無GMS手機要用到真正完整GMS就一定要Root過部機先算真正使用Android 裡面嘅Google完整服務。<br />\n<br />\n尋晚佢條片又呃到更多藍絲變On9&hellip; 你一個On9好，仲要出片誤導人&hellip;好彩信佢嘅多數係藍絲。"},{"pid":"8060ddb498628aa76f78d736bc81f23b8ffc27c6","tid":1613223,"uid":28604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6f6f2cff7cf1699ffe993f740dcb978ad34e1090","tid":1613223,"uid":35347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ccbc5ec548858288058b456d6aae57bb076583b3","tid":1613223,"uid":18947,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8fae32a9824242a3635e207927b0dc9beabe5c13","tid":1613223,"uid":11428,"li